review: I’d like to thank Dr.Keerthana Ashwin who is a friendly and a positive person. She handled the situation in a polite manner and encouraged throughout my Pregnancy Journey. tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Value for money,Treatment satisfaction,
context: Labor and Delivery,Prenatal Checkup,Pregnancy Tests,Pregnancy Check Up,
review:
Now I’m consulting with  Dr Keerthana madam at DFMC  for pas 9 months. I in my journey of pregnancy she has played a major role to make it this journey joyful.  She is very friendly. 
Every visit she explains everything very minutely and very clearly. She clarifies every doubt what we ask her. She is very positive always and cheerful which makes every visit wonderful. 
Even the staff members are very helpful and welcoming at every visit. 
The ambiance of the DFMC is neat and clean. Even this being covid times all norms are followed and patients Care is kept at top most priority. 
Most of the scan and vaccine with medicine is available at one roof so we need not to roam and search for. All facilities are excellent and at par to the expectation. 
I thank doctor and have all regards and best wishes for DFMC progress  from bottom of my heart.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: Doctor behaviour, friendliness, soft spoken, great listener, understanding all issues, providing best advise/treatment and always available in case of emergency - These all points are the key requirements for any patients. Dr Keerthana Mam has all these qualities and my personal experience is I took best decision to start consultation with her. She is pro-active in treating/advising her patients and highlight all issues with all best possible treatments. Thank You Mam for providing best services!!!

My husband and I truly believe in DFMC’s outstanding service with respect to following areas:
